        where 1=1

			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

1576725425--SELECT  count(1) as count FROM u13123456789_product a
        left join u13123456789_product_sku b on a.prd_id=b.prd_id
        where 1=1
1576725425--SELECT b.pic_path as sku_pic_path,a.pic_path,a.prd_id,(case when b.prd_sku_no != '' then b.prd_sku_no else a.prd_no end) as prd_no,a.title,a.price,b.prd_sku_id,b.prd_sku_no,ifnull(b.sku_name1,'') as sku_name1,ifnull(b.sku_name2,'') as sku_name2,a.market,a.floor,a.booth,a.style_no,a.booth_price,a.cus_no,c.wms_qty FROM u13123456789_product a
        left join u13123456789_product_sku b on a.prd_id=b.prd_id
		left join (select prd_id,prd_sku_id,sum(qty) as wms_qty from u13123456789_prdt_wms_qty group by prd_id,prd_sku_id) as c on c.prd_id=b.prd_id and c.prd_sku_id=b.prd_sku_id
        where 1=1
        ORDER BY a.prd_id,b.prd_sku_id limit 0,10
1576725425--
				select COUNT(1) as count from (
					select 1 from u13123456789_product_online where have_sku= '0' 
					union all
					select 1 from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
					inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
					where 1=1 
					
				) a
1576725425--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (

				union all

				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

        ORDER BY a.prd_id,b.prd_sku_id limit 0,10

1576739199--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

1576740333--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid

1576741033--SELECT b.pic_path as sku_pic_path,a.pic_path,a.prd_id,(case when b.prd_sku_no != '' then b.prd_sku_no else a.prd_no end) as prd_no,a.title,a.price,b.prd_sku_id,b.prd_sku_no,ifnull(b.sku_name1,'') as sku_name1,ifnull(b.sku_name2,'') as sku_name2,a.market,a.floor,a.booth,a.style_no,a.booth_price,a.cus_no,c.wms_qty FROM u13123456789_product a
        left join u13123456789_product_sku b on a.prd_id=b.prd_id
		left join (select prd_id,prd_sku_id,sum(qty) as wms_qty from u13123456789_prdt_wms_qty group by prd_id,prd_sku_id) as c on c.prd_id=b.prd_id and c.prd_sku_id=b.prd_sku_id
        where 1=1
        ORDER BY a.prd_id,b.prd_sku_id limit 0,10

1576741033--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10
